OL,3,CFire service concerned wildfire could
OL,4,Cspread to Macclesfield Forest
OL,6,FITV Granada's Rob Smith reports from
OL,7,Fthe scene of the moorland fire.
OL,9,FA huge wildfire has ripped through
OL,10,Fmoorland with thick plumes of smoke
OL,11,Fseen for miles - with firefighters
OL,12,Fconcerned the fire could spread
OL,13,Ftowards nearby Macclesfield Forest.
OL,15,FDramatic video footage shows heavy
OL,16,Fsmoke billowing from land - which is
OL,17,Faround 400 football pitches big - near
OL,18,Fto the Errwood Reservoir, close to the
OL,19,FCat and Fiddle, in the Goyt Valley.
