OL,3,CFire service concerned wildfire could
OL,4,Cspread to Macclesfield Forest
OL,6,FAt its height 10 fire engines from
OL,7,FDerbyshire and Cheshire Fire and
OL,8,FRescue Services were dealing with the
OL,9,Fblaze which broke out around 11:30am
OL,10,Fon Wednesday 30 April.
OL,12,FFirefighters remain on the scene with
OL,13,Fspecialist equipment and are warning
OL,14,Fpeople to stay away from the Goyt
OL,15,FValley area.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/10
