OL,3,CFire service concerned wildfire could
OL,4,Cspread to Macclesfield Forest
OL,6,FDarren Perrott, from Derbyshire Fire
OL,7,Fand Rescue Service said: "The fire has
OL,8,Fnow reached around 320 hectares. It's
OL,9,Fa large fire, it's occured on the
OL,10,Fmoorland and the forestry and
OL,11,Fplantation.
OL,13,FIt's very tinder, it's very dry, it's
OL,14,Fvery ignitable."
OL,16,FHe continued: "We've got indications
OL,17,Fthat it is moving towards the forest.
OL,18,FIt does work for us on this occasion
OL,19,Fbecause we've got a downward slope and
OL,20,Fwe have got crews who can get on top
OL,21,Fof it.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/10
