OL,6,F"However a slight wind direction
OL,7,Fchange and we could be fighting a fire
OL,8,Fin another area."
OL,10,FUnited Utilities have also been
OL,11,Finvolved in the emergency response.
OL,12,FLindsay Page, County Business Leader
OL,13,Ffor Manchester at United Utilities
OL,14,Fsaid: "To contain the fire and
OL,15,Fprioritise public and environmental
OL,16,Fsafety, we have provided a helicopter
OL,17,Fwith the means to transport water from
OL,18,Four local reservoirs to help
OL,19,Fextinguish the flames and minimise
OL,20,Fdamage."
