OL,3,CFire service concerned wildfire could
OL,4,Cspread to Macclesfield Forest
OL,6,F"We have also supplied three of our
OL,7,Fwater tankers to help keep water
OL,8,Fflowing to fire engines, and experts
OL,9,Ffrom our catchment teams are doing all
OL,10,Fthey can to minimise the environmental
OL,11,Fimpact to both the peatlands, and the
OL,12,Fwildlife that call it home."
OL,14,FA road closure has also been put in
OL,15,Fplace near to the Errwood Hall car
OL,16,Fpark, while the historic Cat and
OL,17,FFiddle - a former pub which is now a
OL,18,Fdistillery - also closed, asking
OL,19,Fcustomers to "stay at home" on social
OL,20,Fmedia.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/10
