OL,3,CFire service concerned wildfire could
OL,4,Cspread to Macclesfield Forest
OL,6,FKarl said: "It's pretty scary. We have
OL,7,Four business here, our employees, and
OL,8,Fcustomers too. But I can't thank the
OL,9,Ffire and rescue service enough really,
OL,10,Fthey've been here and reassured us and
OL,11,Fgot on with what they do.
OL,13,F"You look one way and it's beautiful
OL,14,Fblue skies... but you look over
OL,15,FDerbyshire and it's full of smoke.
OL,16,FThere's ash everywhere, fire crews and
OL,17,Fhelicopters... it's been a strange old
OL,18,Fday."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/10
