OL,3,CFire service concerned wildfire could
OL,4,Cspread to Macclesfield Forest
OL,6,FSpeaking on Thursday, Melanie
OL,7,FSelstrom, Marketing Manager at Forest
OL,8,FDistillery said: "It started with a
OL,9,Fcouple of fire engines, then there
OL,10,Fwere five, then there were ten.
OL,12,F"The Cat & Fiddle was built in 1813,
OL,13,Fweathered a lot of storms over the
OL,14,Fyears, but yesterday was really touch
OL,15,Fand go, we were right on the brink of
OL,16,Fwhat could have been devastation.
OL,18,FThere are gas tanks just here, the
OL,19,Fbarns are full of alcohol and ethanol."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/10
